intel:heatmaps-description:1: Heat maps provide individual, match, and community information on your kills, deaths, and areas where you can improve your KD ratio (or EKIA/D). Kill maps show where players were located when they eliminated their enemies. Death maps show where players died the most. KDR maps show areas where players can increase their KDR. Blue areas are where players want to be to get more kills.
